<div class="text-center mb-16">
<span class="text-secondary font-label-md text-label-md tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 block" data-t="reviews_subtitle">Testimonials</span>
<h2 class="text-headline-md font-headline-md text-primary mb-4" data-t="reviews_title">What Our Guests Say</h2>
